snippet.title: Home Safety Hotline: Seasonal Worker | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Home Safety Hotline comes home for the holidays in a new DLC story, launching September 20th! Featuring the talents of Trevor Henderson, Longmont Potion Castle and more!

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2914730/Home_Safety_Hotline_Seasonal_Worker
